<item>
            <title>[PIG-2240] Allow any compression codec to be specified in AvroStorage</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2240</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently it&apos;s only possible to specify deflate - it would be useful to be able to specify Snappy, which Avro now supports.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12520187">PIG-2240</key>
            <summary>Allow any compression codec to be specified in AvroStorage</summary>
